      <title>丹麦部长探讨利用乌克兰基金加速武器生产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/denmark-defense-minister-explores-ukraine-fund-to-hasten-weapons-output</link>
      <description><![CDATA[丹麦国防部长特洛尔斯·伦德·波尔森表示，丹麦正计划设立一个基金来集中投资，扩大乌克兰的武器工业并加快制造速度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/denmark-defense-minister-explores-ukraine-fund-to-hasten-weapons-output</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 13:29:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>舒尔茨宣布向乌克兰提供 14 亿欧元军事援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/scholz-unveils-more-military-aid-for-ukraine-worth-1-4-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨表示，德国和三个欧洲盟友将在年底前向乌克兰提供价值约 14 亿欧元（15 亿美元）的额外军事援助，包括防空系统、作战坦克和榴弹炮。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/scholz-unveils-more-military-aid-for-ukraine-worth-1-4-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 13:23:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>双重风暴将气候问题推入美国总统竞选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/double-punch-storms-thrust-climate-into-the-us-presidential-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[飓风海伦和米尔顿的袭击使得应对气候灾害成为竞选最后几周的一个主要议题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/double-punch-storms-thrust-climate-into-the-us-presidential-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 13:20:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列央行称 2025 年预算是制定利率路径的关键</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/israel-s-central-bank-says-2025-budget-key-to-setting-rate-path</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列央行正在加大对总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡政府的压力，要求其在明年的预算中采取以增长为重点的方针，同时考虑是否通过加息来应对通胀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/israel-s-central-bank-says-2025-budget-key-to-setting-rate-path</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 11:13:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫桑比克民众等待选举结果，反对派叫苦不迭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/mozambicans-await-election-results-as-opposition-cries-foul</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫桑比克选举当局继续汇总周三大选的结果，反对党候选人维南西奥·蒙德拉内声称投票日和随后的计票过程中存在大量违规行为。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/mozambicans-await-election-results-as-opposition-cries-foul</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 11:07:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本首相石破茂首次出访海外 暗示政策延续性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/japan-s-ishiba-signals-continuity-on-first-overseas-trip-as-pm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本新任首相石破茂在老挝举行的地区峰会上承诺深化与韩国的关系，并向中国表达了对两国关系恶化的担忧，以此表明日本政策的连续性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/japan-s-ishiba-signals-continuity-on-first-overseas-trip-as-pm</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 11:07:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>喀麦隆政府禁止就缺席总统的健康状况进行辩论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/cameroon-government-bans-debate-about-absent-president-s-health</link>
      <description><![CDATA[喀麦隆政府禁止媒体讨论总统保罗·比亚的健康状况，自上个月以来，比亚总统一直没有出现在公众视野中，这引发了人们对其健康状况的猜测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/cameroon-government-bans-debate-about-absent-president-s-health</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 11:01:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国将为资金匮乏的发展中国家寻求全球融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/us-to-unveil-proposal-to-prevent-developing-nation-debt-crises</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府即将公布一项计划，向面临现金短缺的发展中国家提供新的融资，目的是防止它们陷入债务危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/us-to-unveil-proposal-to-prevent-developing-nation-debt-crises</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本原子弹幸存者团体获诺贝尔和平奖</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/japan-group-of-atomic-bomb-survivors-gets-nobel-peace-prize</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在核言论达到冷战后顶峰的时代，一群日本原子弹幸存者因其为禁止此类武器所做的努力而获得了诺贝尔和平奖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/japan-group-of-atomic-bomb-survivors-gets-nobel-peace-prize</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 09:05:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列加强对贝鲁特的打击，但尚未与伊朗通话</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/israel-yet-to-reach-iran-decision-as-it-steps-up-beirut-strikes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一名以色列官员称，以色列尚未决定如何对上周伊朗的导弹袭击进行报复，并且仍然受到美国和其他国家的压力，要求其限制报复的严厉程度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/israel-yet-to-reach-iran-decision-as-it-steps-up-beirut-strikes</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 06:58:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
